Name: RestForce
Version: 1.0.0
Summary: A python API for accessing RESTful resources on the force.com platform.
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/RestForce/
Author: Dave Wingate
Author-email: davewingate+restforce@gmail.com
